+	tristate "Allwinner sun8i/sun50i PWM support"
+	depends on ARCH_SUNXI || COMPILE_TEST
+	depends on HAS_IOMEM && COMMON_CLK
+	help
+	  PWM driver for the second-generation Allwinner PWM controller found
+	  in H713, D1, T113, H616, A133 and other sun8i/sun50i SoCs. This
+	  controller supports up to 8 paired channels with independent clock
+	  configuration per pair.
+
+	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the module
+	  will be called pwm-sun8i.
